column16: Brandon Moss singles on a line drive to right fielder Kole Calhoun.   Josh Donaldson to 3rd.

Nick Punto grounds out to first baseman Albert Pujols.

Daniel Robertson out on a sacrifice fly to center fielder Mike Trout.   Ryan Rua scores.
Rougned Odor grounds out, shortstop Erick Aybar to first baseman Albert Pujols.   Ryan Rua to 3rd.
Ryan Rua doubles (5) on a sharp line drive to right fielder Kole Calhoun.
Jesus Guzman flies out to center fielder Mike Trout.
Carlos Corporan called out on strikes.  Jake Marisnick steals (9) 2nd base.
Jake Marisnick singles on a ground ball to center fielder Mike Trout.   Dexter Fowler scores.
Chris Carter grounds out, third baseman David Freese to first baseman C.  J.   Cron.

Jonathan Villar grounds out, second baseman Grant Green to first baseman Efren Navarro.
